data.description: Just the opportunity you have been waiting for!!  Whether you’re a first-time buyer or an investor, this full brick home nestled in at the end of a private cul de sac is waiting for you to make your own!   3 nice-sized bedrooms perfect for use as a primary & guest bedroom PLUS an office for those who work from home.   Spacious den and large flat tree lined backyard perfect for entertaining.  New Roof in 2021.  Added bonus – this home has no HOA making it a great investment property in booming Gastonia.   Enjoy being minutes from the hot FUSE District and Baseball Stadium and the convenience of being approximately 15 minutes from the airport and 30 minutes from Uptown Charlotte.
